Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.50,0:00:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 卡萊多之星要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.50,0:00:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀看卡萊多之星的時候請保持室內的亮度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.70,0:00:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.00,0:00:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那麼 那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.20,0:00:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也有過知道是不好的卻還是做了的經歷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.40,0:00:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣 只要之後好好反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.70,0:00:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說聲“對不起”的話大家也都會諒解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.60,0:00:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利先生也對過去的錯誤好好道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.60,0:00:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是大家重要的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.10,0:00:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很久前好像發生過什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.50,0:00:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊恩 索菲 還有天使的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.60,0:00:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3年前 到底發生了什麼呢 呢 呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.60,0:02:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.20,0:02:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像時間一下就過去了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.70,0:02:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到要結束了就覺得很寂寞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.20,0:02:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.10,0:02:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們 快點結束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.70,0:02:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很受歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.10,0:02:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健 該你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,France
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.80,0:02:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀眾的笑臉 真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.00,0:02:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團差不多也要開始準備再營業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.20,0:02:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.30,0:03:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃什麼啊 還是老樣子 真悠閒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回舞臺的話 就做些什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.70,0:03:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如抓住老闆的弱點之類啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種方法……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.20,0:03:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了你在諾瓦路馬戲團的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新站起來了呢 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.80,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 真的給由利先生添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊 由利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.90,0:03:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利先生也去卡萊多劇團嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.70,0:03:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 卡洛斯委託我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新複出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.30,0:03:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為舞臺導演兼演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.30,0:03:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可喜可賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複出的人不止我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 那樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.60,0:04:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利那樣說了 沒事的沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 老闆 老闆……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從由利先生那裏聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.70,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我回舞臺 我已經……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 再簽約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.20,0:04:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.20,0:04:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管什麼角色 都會盡力去演的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.00,0:04:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的角色已經決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅也進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.10,0:04:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的新作 由我來當舞臺的導演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇名是天鵝湖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.90,0:04:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔任主角公主的 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 沒反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.40,0:04:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嚷嚷了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.80,0:04:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在法國 我一直在調查關於真正的明星的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.60,0:04:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空遇到一個叫亞蘭的男人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.10,0:04:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.90,0:04:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教萊恩的妹妹索菲天使的絕技的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.30,0:05:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 完成天使的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.90,0:05:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要誕生出真正的明星的事你也知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從以前認識亞蘭的人那裏聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.80,0:05:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的絕技是通往真正的明星之路的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有同感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.10,0:05:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在雜技大賽時教了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是真的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了空的天使的絕技的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.10,0:05:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為心靈應該相通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.80,0:05:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻沒有那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.50,0:05:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有想過那是不是真正的明星的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.10,0:05:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但實際遇見亞蘭後 終於能聽到那問題的答案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.70,0:05:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個天使的絕技並沒有完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指完美版的天使的絕技嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.80,0:05:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的絕技還有後文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望讓空在這個舞臺上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.80,0:06:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成完美版的天使的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.60,0:06:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鵝湖的高潮部分由天使的絕技來表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.20,0:06:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那舞臺上發掘出真正的卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.70,0:06:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.00,0:06:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了成為你的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.70,0:06:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我叫來這裏 就是為了說我“已經沒用了”吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.40,0:06:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說就你能教授天使的絕技嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.80,0:06:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑你的話能教嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.40,0:06:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就把話說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.20,0:06:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來期待著被稱為死神的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但按照至今為止來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.10,0:06:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃避了與空的搭配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不放棄對你的期待了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我在逃避？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘是在逃避吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.60,0:06:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的絕技的特訓不也是中途放棄了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有自信的話就隨便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然逃避了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個無能的膽小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.80,0:07:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以連對我的復仇也做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這個秋千
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒見過的形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩排時臨時用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.70,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的絕技 要用這個秋千
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會做出怎樣的動作呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.90,0:07:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想演一下 就用這秋千
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱西小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 突然來訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.90,0:07:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.90,0:07:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我的樣子 是像來美亞家來住的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.60,0:07:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像……像吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了天鵝湖的企劃了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐立不安呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和美亞一起 徹底的探討一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.70,0:08:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 靈感有了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.70,0:08:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才剛剛聽說 還沒開始考慮……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 已經過了1小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.70,0:08:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然什麼都沒考慮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.60,0:08:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的什麼都沒考慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.90,0:08:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.10,0:08:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 要不要先來杯茶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.50,0:08:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該有靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.50,0:08:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在正式公演的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健有他自己的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能依賴健的天然派角色了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漢娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.00,0:08:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.90,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴貝拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.10,0:08:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能想出什麼好的道具嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.60,0:08:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行呢 這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.10,0:08:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次相信了 結果你們慘死了……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好考慮一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 阿娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.80,0:08:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了調查天使的絕技花了不少功夫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說 挑戰的記錄太少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.70,0:08:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.10,0:09:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過長期的非常人的嚴格訓練之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.30,0:09:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演卻有失華麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.70,0:09:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都認為挑戰那種東西的是愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.40,0:09:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就連那是什麼絕技 都幾乎沒人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.50,0:09:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑戰天使的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果失敗的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.10,0:09:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待你的只有嘲笑聲而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.70,0:09:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要走這條路嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確信嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.10,0:09:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是通往真正的明星的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.80,0:09:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此 我現在也只是想挑戰這個絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後會發生什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.90,0:09:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.30,0:09:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想不經嘗試就後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.50,0:09:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父母留下幼小的我去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.30,0:09:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有各種想做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.20,0:09:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得他們應該十分遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.40,0:10:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要去嘗試做任何事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.30,0:10:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.60,0:10:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲小姐沒能完成天使的絕技的那份遺憾 我很瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.60,0:10:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.50,0:10:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道索菲的死因嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.90,0:10:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被我殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.70,0:10:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前的雜技大賽 即將來臨之季
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.30,0:10:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶然看到萊恩和索菲練習的天使的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.60,0:10:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個一看就知道是個未完成的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.70,0:10:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然是個不能威脅到蕾拉的黃金不死鳥取得優勝的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.60,0:10:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那時我所懼怕的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.90,0:10:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊恩的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.00,0:10:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果卡洛斯叫萊恩加入卡萊多劇團的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為我的立場就危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.80,0:11:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那時的我有個野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放逐把父親逼上死亡的卡洛斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.90,0:11:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪取卡萊多劇團這個野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜技大賽當天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.80,0:11:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把她叫到遠離會場的公園裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.50,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙她說有話和她說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.30,0:11:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就一直等待著不可能出現的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.00,0:11:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至勉強能趕上雜技大賽的時間才回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她回去的路上 遇到了事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.90,0:11:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院裏的萊恩打來好幾次電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.50,0:11:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說在索菲斷氣前 希望能讓我去見她一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.80,0:11:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭著求了我好幾遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲崇拜著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.30,0:11:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 說一聲你不是騙她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.00,0:11:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓她帶著受傷的心而死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.50,0:11:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了……求你了……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.30,0:12:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要表演的我 怎麼可能去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.80,0:12:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利先生…… 那種事……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.60,0:12:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隨時都能成為惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.40,0:12:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能培育出天使的 只有真正的惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.60,0:12:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空要成為天使的話 就必須得接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為惡魔的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.50,0:12:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備和萊恩一決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.60,0:12:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成為真正惡魔的人 就是空的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.70,0:12:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利的雙魚座 和 萊恩的天蠍座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.60,0:12:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前所未有的激烈鬥爭 即將開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很久都沒輪到空做主角了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.90,0:12:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果梅不在的話就……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 空 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.40,0:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給梅看看實力差距啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.50,0:13:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我行李很少呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<缺翻譯>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能回自己原來的屋子 真太好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.90,0:13:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是謝謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.10,0:13:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢 大家都很期待著空做主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.90,0:13:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那是很高興 不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.80,0:13:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是想讓大家和梅和平相處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.00,0:13:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 都是站在同一舞臺上表演的夥伴嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美亞她們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.90,0:13:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛吉特在……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.80,0:13:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道會是這樣 真慶倖事先做了準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.10,0:13:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要進去了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 請進請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進到裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛吉特也來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.90,0:13:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 不用進到那麼裏面……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可樂喝嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.30,0:14:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正要開複出慶祝會之類的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會去參加的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子好遲鈍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.00,0:14:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是乾杯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.00,0:14:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備通過這次的舞臺 讓我看到你真正的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.60,0:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡全力演好奧迪路這個角色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.30,0:14:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓公主的光芒完全蓋過我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.90,0:14:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.80,0:14:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果你做不好的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.60,0:14:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會隨時去搶主角的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.50,0:14:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到了射手座的光輝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.60,0:14:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金牛座的光輝又更增光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.30,0:14:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說乾杯不如說是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的做法啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦！搖搖搖搖搖搖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.80,0:14:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！一時還以為會……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.10,0:14:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒有爭鬥的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.00,0:14:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.40,0:15:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你是把我打敗 得到了主角的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會在以後把你打敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.80,0:15:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那回事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.20,0:15:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 大概是和梅是成為夥伴了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.41,0:15:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不覺得在跟妳競爭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不像之前那樣就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.31,0:15:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要也跟其他人做朋友？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.18,0:15:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了\N跟那些光說不練的垃圾？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.65,0:15:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會那樣的，大家都很拼命喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們再去舞台一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.80,0:15:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看妳的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.93,0:15:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為明天就要練習啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真高興你沒有逃避呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.86,0:16:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要給你報仇的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.60,0:16:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你恨我把蘇菲害死對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.94,0:16:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拿起那把劍跟我打吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.48,0:16:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，辦不到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.18,0:16:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就揭穿死神的真面目吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.62,0:16:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不是死神\N也並沒有在找搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.89,0:16:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這三年你只是在確認\N沒有任何人能取代蘇菲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且藉此安心罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是空出現在你的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.04,0:16:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該早就察覺到\N空的能力甚至超越蘇菲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.14,0:16:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為她應該能通過\N天使絕技的考驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.85,0:17:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此才突然對空進行特訓\N希望她可以主動放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.58,0:17:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而無論如何空都沒有放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你也開始感到恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.66,0:17:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去將要進行\N天使絕技的特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.49,0:17:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來你必須承認自己\N是無法成為惡魔的懦夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.63,0:17:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.10,0:17:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲之所以沒有成為天使\N是因為你沒完全化為惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.27,0:17:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你而言比起蘇菲成為天使\N進行無謂特訓的日子更為重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.51,0:17:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣才能避免讓別人\N知道你有多麼懦弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.15,0:17:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲死後最安心的應該是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.36,0:17:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.92,0:17:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為可以隱瞞你騙她的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.13,0:17:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.03,0:17:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感謝我吧，里昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.20,0:17:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你從痛苦中解放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲的夢想是沈重的負擔對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就承認吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.67,0:18:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准再說了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.28,0:18:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時間？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算跟里昂算清舊帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.99,0:18:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能成為真正惡魔的人\N就會成為空的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.70,0:18:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲或許早就知道你的本性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.74,0:18:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.47,0:18:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.37,0:19:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.61,0:19:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.85,0:19:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都快住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.96,0:19:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是舞台啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.19,0:19:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在舞台上傷害對方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.36,0:19:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論誰將成為我的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.57,0:19:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要這樣才能完成的天使絕技…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種的根本就沒有意義！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.74,0:19:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不知道舞台在傷心嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.55,0:19:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是充滿爭執與憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.82,0:19:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舞台一定會傷心的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.72,0:19:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟蘇菲說的一樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.43,0:20:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她約定過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.60,0:20:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要完成天使絕技\N讓她成為真正的巨星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.50,0:20:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的巨星會讓舞台充滿笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.57,0:20:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的心將會合而為一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.64,0:20:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演員跟觀眾都會像是一家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我約定好吧，里昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.86,0:20:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲…蘇菲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.83,0:20:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.44,0:20:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我沒有自信是否能讓\N真正的巨星誕生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.18,0:20:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲夢想中沒有競爭的舞台\N我根本就無法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.82,0:21:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到最後只留下這個約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.42,0:21:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有空能實現這個約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.13,0:21:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能將空培育成天使的只有里昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.10,0:21:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在三年前蘇菲死後\N你的時間就停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.57,0:21:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能藉由報復我\N讓你的時間重新運轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.45,0:21:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算藉此贖罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.65,0:21:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是對蘇菲…或是蕾拉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真笨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.15,0:21:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.52,0:21:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特地叫我來就是為了這個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.59,0:21:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有必要對我贖罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.53,0:21:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初優勝的價值並沒有改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.70,0:21:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐知道蘇菲小姐的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.67,0:21:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛聽尤里說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.37,0:21:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有競爭的舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.64,0:21:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲似乎也希望不藉由競爭\N成為真正的巨星呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.34,0:22:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我並不相信這種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.21,0:22:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道了一件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.35,0:22:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.22,0:22:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個重要的東西\N忘記在舞台上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.99,0:22:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧，尤里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.49,0:22:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里昂會成為空的搭檔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.73,0:22:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想履行約定的話\N這將是最後的機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.94,0:22:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.75,0:22:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,匆促聚集而來的不幸\N流逝的時間已經終結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.25,0:22:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如預告 放輕鬆吧\N現在馬上就帶你走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.46,0:22:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快一點 我們走吧\N強迫前進 最快速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.50,0:22:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俯視日常的最佳視野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.97,0:22:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夕陽的落點 我的最愛\N港灣燈光 繁星夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.74,0:23:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了明天 從煩惱中逃脫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.48,0:23:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有休假也想獲得綠洲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.28,0:23:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關掉手機用愛來充電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.32,0:23:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只以溫柔無法治癒\N因為還留有痛楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.56,0:23:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是寂寞的 擦肩而過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.83,0:23:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將會發生什麼？\N在誤會盡頭邂逅的真心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.77,0:23:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使哭泣或微笑\N我都會伴隨著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.61,0:23:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.45,0:23:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在感覺到的是嫉妒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.79,0:23:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此我選擇了不同的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.52,0:23:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且跟命運中的那個人重逢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.89,0:23:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，我跟蕾拉小姐\N都是從那裡開始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.86,0:23:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天的感動是千真萬確的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.60,0:24:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集的萬花筒之星\N飛舞降臨的最純真天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.57,0:24:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羽翼是夢想，然後飛向天空
